          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>From <strong>Prada</strong> and <strong>Stella McCartney</strong> to the <strong>Lucia Bag</strong> for <strong>Borbonese</strong> at <strong>Milan Fashion Week 2020</strong>, recognised by <strong>Vogue Italia</strong> among Italy's Top 5 Foreign Designers in 2024.</p>"
          }
        },
        "quote": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "text": "AKINNA is the result of years spent chasing one perfect spark — a vision of modern luxury that feels personal, timeless, and deeply meaningful."
          }
